title: Erikslusts Pizzeria
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Pizza, Italian, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Ordinary pizzeria (with gambling machines, fake brick walls and plastic plants), which offer a good range of vegan choices such as vegan faux gyros, salami, minced meat, ham, tuna, in addition to vegan cheeses. As is common in Swedish pizzerias you will be offered pizzasallad, which is shredded cole in vinegar and oregano at no charge.
